<P>
   EDs: This is the CoxNet Books page for the current week. This
layout is available now.COXNET BOOKS 0805: A FUTURE WITH e-BOOKS _
E-books are pieces of hardware about the size of a typical
paperback novel that store digital text and graphics, much like a
computer. Their turning some heads in the publishing world, but
many readers still want to turn pages. (Moore, Austin
American-Statesman) Art includes a 4-column color photo
