<P>
   REVIEW MOTHER _ Thanks to Spencer Tracy and Steve Martin, the
plight of the father of the bride has been amply documented. But
what about Mom? Joan Bennett and even Diane Keaton, for Pete's
sake, seemed to take it all so calmly, totally in control at all
times. According to certified m.o.b. Ilene Beckerman, don't believe
