   SPORTS
</P>
<P>
   TANK _ Almost overnight, sports agent William ``Tank'' Black
leaped from having one major client to more than 35. Suddenly the
once-broke former assistant football coach from South Carolina was
buying a brick mansion, leasing a private jet at $3,000 per hour
and giving expensive gifts to an exotic dancer who was not his
wife. (Elmore, Palm Beach Post) 65. MOVED.
