<HEADLINE>
`MICROPOWER': ELECTRICITY PRODUCED, LITERALLY, IN YOUR BACKYARD  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (NOTE 325-word trim; 1,075 uncut)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 750-word (trimmed) material from The
