<HEADLINE>
GORE LISTS REASONS FOR PICKING ANY OF THOSE ON SHORT LIST 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By JILL ZUCKMAN AND SUSAN MILLIGAN  
 c.2000 The Boston Globe  
 
