<HEADLINE>
U.S. OLYMPIC SWIMMING BIOS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By GIL LEBRETON 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
 
 
 
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Where: Indianapolis When:Wednesday-Aug. 16 Venue: IU Natatorium
(capacity 6,200), located on the campus of Indiana
University-Purdue University Indianapolis (IUPUI) Who: Nearly 1,300
swimmers who have achieved qualifying standards in 13 men's and
women's events Who makes the Olympic team: Top two finishers in
each event. The top six in the 100 and 200 freestyle will qualify
for the relay teams. \Nsubheds:Who to watch \Nagatea: MEN Lenny
Krayzelburg
</P>
<P>
   24 years old
</P>
<P>
   Height: 6-2
</P>
<P>
   Weight: 180
</P>
<P>
   Hometown: Odessa, Russia
</P>
<P>
   Resides: Studio City, Calif.
</P>
<P>
   College: Southern Cal '98
</P>
<P>
   Holds world records in the 50-, 100- and 200-meter backstroke
... owns six of the 10 fastest times ever in the 200 back ...
ranked first in the world in 50, 100 and 200 back in 1999 ... named
USA Swimming's 1999 Swimmer of the Year ... born in the Ukraine,
came to the U.S. with parents in 1989 ... became U.S. citizen in
1995. Neil Walker
</P>
<P>
   24 years old
</P>
<P>
   Height: 6-4
</P>
<P>
   Weight: 185
</P>
<P>
   Hometown: Verona, Wis.
</P>
<P>
   Resides: Austin
</P>
<P>
   College: Texas '98
</P>
<P>
   Won 50m and 100m free and 100m back at Spring Nationals ... won
seven medals and broke five world records and 10 American records
at Short Course World Championships in March in Athens, Greece ...
'97 NCAA Swimmer of Year ... swims for Texas Aquatics club. Ed
Moses
</P>
<P>
   20 years old
</P>
<P>
   Height: 5-10
</P>
<P>
   Weight: 170
</P>
<P>
   Hometown: Burke, Va.
</P>
<P>
   Resides: Burke, Va.
</P>
<P>
   College: Virginia '02
</P>
<P>
   Broke world records three times at NCAA Championships ... won
100-meter breaststroke in world record time of 57.66 at NCAAs,
after breaking world record in prelims ... also won NCAA 200-meter
breast in world record time of 2:06.40 ... won '99 Pan Am Games 100
breast ... didn't start swimming year-round until senior year of
high school. Tom Dolan
</P>
<P>
   24 years old
</P>
<P>
   Height: 6-6
</P>
<P>
   Weight: 180
</P>
