   College: Michigan '98
</P>
<P>
   Won gold medal in 400-meter individual medley at Atlanta
Olympics ... world record-holder (4:12.30) in the 400 IM ... USA
Swimming's Swimmer of the Year in '94 and '95 ... underwent knee
surgery in May 1999 and missed most of last season ... appeared on
Wheaties box after '96 Olympics. WOMEN Jenny Thompson
</P>
