</P>
<P>
   World record-holder (57.88 seconds) in 100-meter butterfly ...
owns five Olympic gold medals and six medals overall. . . has three
of four fastest times ever in 100 fly ... named 1999 U.S. Olympic
Committee's SportsWoman of the Year ... tied with speedskater
